<p><b>Amor Ben Salem</b> (<a href="/wiki/Arabic_language" title="Arabic language">Arabic</a>: <span lang="ar" dir="rtl" xml:lang="ar">عمر بن سالم</span>‎) is a <a href="/wiki/Tunisian_people" title="Tunisian people" class="mw-redirect">Tunisian</a> Arabic writer.</p>
<p></p>
